data.description: This spacious stately 4 bed, 3.50 bath with a bonus room downstairs and a bonus room in the garage is located in a cul-da-sac next to a board walk and nature trail that leads to a stocked pond. The home features transferable new home warranty with 23' ceilings in living room, large walk in master closet, slab granite throughout, wood flooring, stainless steel appliances, and a community playground. Wired for hung TVs throughout and high tech security system available.
